events.name: A320_Neo_FCU_VS_DEC
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT VERTICAL HOLD VAR:3, feet per minute) 100 - -6000 max (>K:2:AP_VS_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:A320_Neo_FCU_VS_DEC) (>H:A320_Neo_FCU_VS_HOLD)

events.name: A320_Neo_FCV_VS_INC
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT VERTICAL HOLD VAR:3, feet per minute) 100 + 6000 min (>K:2:AP_VS_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:A320_Neo_FCU_VS_INC) (>H:A320_Neo_FCU_VS_HOLD)

events.name: ASOA320_MASTER_BATTERY_1_OFF
events.script: (A:ELECTRICAL MASTER BATTERY:1, Bool) if{ 1 (>K:TOGGLE_MASTER_BATTERY) } 0 sp0 10 (>A:BUS LOOKUP INDEX, Number) (A:BUS CONNECTION ON:6, Bool) l0 != if{ 10 6 (>K:2:ELECTRICAL_BUS_TO_BUS_CONNECTION_TOGGLE) }

events.name: ASOA320_MASTER_BATTERY_1_ON
events.script: (A:ELECTRICAL MASTER BATTERY:1, Bool) ! if{ 1 (>K:TOGGLE_MASTER_BATTERY) } 1 sp0 10 (>A:BUS LOOKUP INDEX, Number) (A:BUS CONNECTION ON:6, Bool) l0 != if{ 10 6 (>K:2:ELECTRICAL_BUS_TO_BUS_CONNECTION_TOGGLE) }

events.name: ASOA320_APU_MASTER_SW_OFF
events.script: // Turn OFF APU Fuel Valve // If valve is ON (1), toggle it to OFF (0) (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 1 == if{  8 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_TOGGLE) } // Additionally turn off the APU in case valve is off afterwards (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 0 == if{  (>K:APU_OFF_SWITCH) }

events.name: ASOA320_APU_MASTER_SW_ON
events.script: // Turn ON APU Fuel Valve // If valve is off (0), toggle it to ON (1) (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 0 == if{  8 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_TOGGLE) }

events.name: APU_MASTER_SW_OFF
events.script: // Turn OFF APU Fuel Valve // If valve is ON (1), toggle it to OFF (0) (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 1 == if{  8 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_TOGGLE) } // Additionally turn off the APU in case valve is off afterwards (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 0 == if{  (>K:APU_OFF_SWITCH) }

events.name: APU_MASTER_SW_ON
events.script: // Turn ON APU Fuel Valve // If valve is off (0), toggle it to ON (1) (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:8, Bool) 0 == if{  8 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_TOGGLE) }

events.name: A32NX_OH_NOSE_LIGHTS_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1, Number) ++ 3 % s0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1) l0 0 == if{ 1 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) quit } l0 1 == if{ 0 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 1 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) quit } 0 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET)

events.name: A32NX_OVHD_STROBE_LIGHTS_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0, Number) ++ 3 % s0 (>L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0, Number) l0 0 == if{ 0 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) quit } l0 1 == if{ 1 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) quit } 0 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 0 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET)

events.name: All_Exterior_Lights_-_In_Flight
events.script: 0 (>L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0) 0 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:BEACON_LIGHTS_SET) 0 0 s0 (>K:2:WING_LIGHTS_SET) l0 (>L:LIGHTING_WING_0) 0 1 (>K:2:NAV_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:LOGO_LIGHTS_SET) 0 s0 (>L:LIGHTING_TAXI_2) 2 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 3 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 1 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 1 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1) 0 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET)

events.name: All_Exterior_Lights_-_Park_Parking
events.script: 1 (>L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0) 1 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:BEACON_LIGHTS_SET) 0 0 s0 (>K:2:WING_LIGHTS_SET) l0 (>L:LIGHTING_WING_0) 0 1 (>K:2:NAV_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:LOGO_LIGHTS_SET) 0 s0 (>L:LIGHTING_TAXI_2) 2 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 3 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 1 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 1 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1) 0 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET)

events.name: All_Exterior_Lights_-_Take_Off
events.script: 0 (>L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0) 0 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:BEACON_LIGHTS_SET) 0 0 s0 (>K:2:WING_LIGHTS_SET) l0 (>L:LIGHTING_WING_0) 0 1 (>K:2:NAV_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:LOGO_LIGHTS_SET) 0 s0 (>L:LIGHTING_TAXI_2) 2 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 3 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 0 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 1 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 0 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 1 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1) 1 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET)

events.name: All_Exterior_Lights_-_Taxi
events.script: 1 (>L:LIGHTING_STROBE_0) 1 (>L:STROBE_0_Auto) 1 0 r (>K:2:STROBES_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:BEACON_LIGHTS_SET) 0 0 s0 (>K:2:WING_LIGHTS_SET) l0 (>L:LIGHTING_WING_0) 0 1 (>K:2:NAV_LIGHTS_SET) 0 1 (>K:2:LOGO_LIGHTS_SET) 1 s0 (>L:LIGHTING_TAXI_2) 2 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 3 l0 (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 1 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 1 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 1 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_1) 0 1 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) 1 1 r (>K:2:TAXI_LIGHTS_SET)

events.name: LANDING_LIGHTS_L_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2, Number) 0 == if{ 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 1 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) } els{ (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2, Number) 1 == if{ 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 0 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 1 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } els{ 1 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 0 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } }

events.name: LANDING_LIGHTS_L_R_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2, Number) 0 == if{ 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 1 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 1 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) } els{ (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2, Number) 1 == if{ 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 0 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 1 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 0 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 1 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } els{ 1 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_2) 0 (>L:LANDING_2_Retracted) 0 2 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  1 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 0 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } }

events.name: LANDING_LIGHTS_R_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3, Number) 0 == if{ 2 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 1 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET) } els{ (L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3, Number) 1 == if{ 0 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 0 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 1 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } els{ 1 (>L:LIGHTING_LANDING_3) 0 (>L:LANDING_3_Retracted) 0 3 r (>K:2:LANDING_LIGHTS_SET)  } }

events.name: A32NX_OVHD_RCDR_GND_CTL_TOGGLE
events.script: (L:A32NX_RCDR_GROUND_CONTROL_ON,bool) ! if{ (A:GENERAL ENG OIL PRESSURE:1, psi) 18 < sp1  (A:GENERAL ENG OIL PRESSURE:2, psi) 18 < sp2  (L:A32NX_ELEC_DC_ESS_SHED_BUS_IS_POWERED,bool) l1 and l2 and  if{ 1 (>L:A32NX_RCDR_GROUND_CONTROL_ON,bool) } } els{ 0 (>L:A32NX_RCDR_GROUND_CONTROL_ON,bool) }

events.name: ATC_Custom_Btn_CLR
events.script: (L:XPNDR_clr) s1 2 < if{ (L:XPNDR_pos) -- s0 0 < if{ 3 } els{ l0 } (>L:XPNDR_pos) l1 0 == if{ (A:TRANSPONDER CODE:1,number) } els{ (L:XPNDR_temp) } 10 div (>L:XPNDR_temp) 2 (>L:XPNDR_clr) } els{ 0 (>L:XPNDR_temp) 0 (>L:XPNDR_pos) } (>H:A320_Neo_ATC_BTN_CLR) (E:SIMULATION TIME,second) 7 + (>L:XPNDR_timeout)

events.name: ISIS_KNOB_ANTICLOCKWISE
events.script: (L:A32NX_ISIS_BUGS_ACTIVE, enum) 1 == if{ 0 (>H:A32NX_ISIS_KNOB_ANTI_CLOCKWISE) } els{ (L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_MODE, enum) 1 != if{  (L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_UNIT_INHG, enum) if {  3 (>K:KOHLSMAN_DEC) } els{  3 (A:KOHLSMAN SETTING MB:3, millibars) -- 16 * (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET)  }  } }

events.name: ISIS_KNOB_CLOCKWISE
events.script: (L:A32NX_ISIS_BUGS_ACTIVE, enum) 1 == if{ 0 (>H:A32NX_ISIS_KNOB_CLOCKWISE) } els{ (L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_MODE, enum) 1 != if{  (L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_UNIT_INHG, enum) if {  3 (>K:KOHLSMAN_INC) } els{  3 (A:KOHLSMAN SETTING MB:3, millibars) ++ 16 * (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET)  }  } }

events.name: ISIS_KNOB_PRESSED
events.script: (L:A32NX_ISIS_BUGS_ACTIVE, bool) if{  0 (>H:A32NX_ISIS_KNOB_PRESSED, number) } els{  (L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_MODE, enum) 0 == if{  1 (>L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_MODE, enum) (A:KOHLSMAN SETTING MB:2, bars) 16000 * (>0:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_SAVED, number) 2 16211 (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET) } els{  0 (>L:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_MODE, enum) 2 (0:A32NX_ISIS_BARO_SAVED, number) (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET) } }

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_DEC
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) - (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) % - (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) % + 100 max (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Down) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_DEC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_DEC100
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 100 - 100 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 100 % - 100 % + 100 max (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Down) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_DEC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_DEC1000
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 1000 - 1000 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 1000 % - 1000 % + 1000 max (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Down) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_DEC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_INC
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) + (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) (L:XMLVAR_Autopilot_Altitude_Increment) % - 49000 min (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Up) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_INC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_INC100
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 100 + (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 100 % - 49000 min (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Up) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_INC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_INC1000
events.script: 3 (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 1000 + (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR:3, feet) 1000 % - 49000 min (>K:2:AP_ALT_VAR_SET_ENGLISH) (>H:AP_KNOB_Up) (>H:A320_Neo_CDU_AP_INC_ALT)

events.name: A32NX_FCU_ALT_PUSH_PULL_TOGGLE
events.script: (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE SLOT INDEX, Number) 1 == if{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_ALT_PUSH) } els{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_ALT_PULL) }

events.name: A32NX_FCU_HDG_Push_Pull_Toggle
events.script: (A:AUTOPILOT HEADING SLOT INDEX, Number) 1 == if{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_HDG_PUSH) } els{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_HDG_PULL) }

events.name: A32NX_FCU_SPEED_PUSH_PULL_TOGGLE
events.script: (A:AUTOPILOT SPEED SLOT INDEX, Number) 1 == if{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_SPD_PUSH) } els{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_SPD_PULL) }

events.name: A32NX_FCU_VS_PUSH_PULL_TOGGLE
events.script: (A:AUTOPILOT VS SLOT INDEX, Number) 1 == if{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_VS_PUSH) } els{ (>K:A32NX.FCU_VS_PULL) }

events.name: A32NX_OH_ELEC_EXTPWR_TOG
events.script: (A:EXTERNAL POWER AVAILABLE:1, Bool) (A:EXTERNAL POWER ON:1, Bool) ! and if{ 1 (>K:TOGGLE_EXTERNAL_POWER) } els{ (A:EXTERNAL POWER ON:1, Bool) if{ 1 (>K:TOGGLE_EXTERNAL_POWER) } }

events.name: A32NX_THROTTLE_FULL_REVERSE_BUTTON
events.script: (A:GENERAL ENG THROTTLE LEVER POSITION:1,percent) -0.1 < if{ -9830 } els{ -16383 } (>K:THROTTLE_SET)

events.name: A32NX_PED_ENG_1_START_LEVER_TOG
events.script: (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:1, Bool) if{ 1 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_CLOSE) (A:GENERAL ENG STARTER:1, Bool) if{ (>K:TOGGLE_STARTER1) } } els{ 1 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_OPEN) (A:GENERAL ENG STARTER:1, Bool) ! if{ (>K:TOGGLE_STARTER1) } }

events.name: A32NX_PED_ENG_2_START_LEVER_TOG
events.script: (A:FUELSYSTEM VALVE SWITCH:2, Bool) if{ 2 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_CLOSE) (A:GENERAL ENG STARTER:2, Bool) if{ (>K:TOGGLE_STARTER2) } } els{ 2 (>K:FUELSYSTEM_VALVE_OPEN) (A:GENERAL ENG STARTER:2, Bool) ! if{ (>K:TOGGLE_STARTER2) } }

events.name: A32NX_OH_DOME_LIGHT_TOGGLE
events.script: (A:LIGHT POTENTIOMETER:7, Percent) 0 == if{ 1 (>K:CABIN_LIGHTS_SET) 20 (>K:LIGHT_POTENTIOMETER_7_SET) } els{ (A:LIGHT POTENTIOMETER:7, Percent) 100 == if{ 0 (>K:CABIN_LIGHTS_SET) 0 (>K:LIGHT_POTENTIOMETER_7_SET) } els{ 1 (>K:CABIN_LIGHTS_SET) 100 (>K:LIGHT_POTENTIOMETER_7_SET) } }

events.name: INI320_EFIS_BARO_CPT_DECR
events.script: (L:XMLVAR_Baro1_Mode) 2 != (L:XMLVAR_Baro1_Mode) 3 != and if{ (L:XMLVAR_Baro_Selector_HPA_1) if{ 1 (A:KOHLSMAN SETTING MB:1, mbars) -- 16 * (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET) } els{ 1 (>K:KOHLSMAN_DEC) } }

events.name: INI320_EFIS_BARO_CPT_INCR
events.script: (L:XMLVAR_Baro1_Mode) 2 != (L:XMLVAR_Baro1_Mode) 3 != and if{ (L:XMLVAR_Baro_Selector_HPA_1) if{ 1 (A:KOHLSMAN SETTING MB:1, mbars) ++ 16 * (>K:2:KOHLSMAN_SET) } els{ 1 (>K:KOHLSMAN_INC) } }
